item.title: CVE-2024-21983|2024-06-07T15:58:32.902Z -- netapp -- storagegrid
item.description: StorageGRID (formerly StorageGRID Webscale) versions prior to 11.8 are susceptible to a Denial of Service (DoS) vulnerability. Successful exploit by an authenticated attacker could lead to an out of memory condition or node reboot.
